 libparse-yapp-perl, openbabel, curl, libhtml-parser-perl, tree, gawk,
 libwww-curl-perl, libjson-perl, ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: tools for manipulating CIF format files
 Package provides a set of tools for manipulating Crystallographic
